---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Transfer Venmo balance to the unique selected standard bank destination

Usage: out [OPTIONS] --speed <SPEED> <AMOUNT>

Arguments:
  <AMOUNT>
          Positive USD amount with at most two fractional digits

Options:
      --speed <SPEED>
          Transfer speed; only standard is currently accepted

          [possible values: standard]

      --yes
          Skip only the final default-No confirmation

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

Confirmation defaults to No. Financial exit code 3 means the transfer outcome must be verified independently. Do not retry; check `activity list` and the official Venmo app. Only standard bank cash-out is supported; inbound, instant, debit, manual destination selection, and challenge continuation remain unavailable.
